{
  "stem": "12674.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It had nothing to do with it with your inner self, because when I came out of there, I was just as innocent as when I went in, because I had decided I wasn't going to sell my-- sell myself for a piece of bread, which I had the opportunity many times to do.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I did not because I chose not to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It had nothing to do with wanting the bread or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I chose to think of myself as something else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this is not-- that's just about the washing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So, so there were-- there were other things that happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was working very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was a very pretty girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm-- now I'm an old lady, but once upon a time, I was a very pretty girl.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, during-- and my father lived someplace else, and I lived in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- Oh, apropos, did I tell you in the barracks, my aunt lived there too, my father's oldest sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was a fantastic woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was so sure that she was there to save the whole world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Her husband was a very big man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He weighed over 200 pounds, and she was a little tiny little woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name was Berthe, and they called her [NON-ENGLISH] because of her daughter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and she gave him all her food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She voluntarily got herself tuberculosis because she felt he was a big man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the little rations that we-- she got, she would say she already ate, and she would give it to her because she was-- he would come to visit her.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she would prepare his food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they would eat together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From wherever he was sleeping, he would come to her room.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
